race.name: KC Masterpiece 400
race.comments: Kevin Harvick won the KC Masterpiece 400 at Kansas Speedway, his 42nd Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series victory. Prior to the start of the race, the following car dropped to the rear of the field for the reason indicated: No. 42 (unapproved tire change).
